# Team Profiles

Headshots and profile images for Bright Interaction team members.

## Usage

### CDN URL (recommended)
```
https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/bright-interaction/assets/profiles/[filename]
```

### Raw URL (alternative)
```
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bright-interaction/assets/main/profiles/[filename]
```

## Current Profiles
- Tom Isgren - Founder & CRM Automation Specialist

## File Naming Convention
Use format: `firstname-lastname-type.jpg`

Examples:
- `tom-isgren-headshot.jpg` - Standard headshot
- `tom-isgren-square.jpg` - Square crop for social media
- `firstname-lastname-casual.jpg` - Casual photo

## Image Specifications
- **Format**: JPG or PNG
- **Headshots**: Minimum 800x800px
- **File size**: Keep under 500KB for email signatures
